{"id": 3114, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你觉得怎样才算是“看进去一部作品”了？", "description": "你的“观看”的门槛是提高了还是降低了？（题图来自：iStock ©️ saemilee ）", "record_count": 4713, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/202001052134526yWYUtBZodrIE3bq.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-05T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6170, "title": "现如今你觉得怎样才算是“看进去一部作品”了？", "content": "现如今你觉得怎样才算是“看进去一部作品”了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 351505, "content": "看 cut/推荐书评之类的感觉不错，顺手 mark 一下", "image": "img/option/option/20200105213756Rg6CSxnkaj7D9qF2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351507, "content": "进度条跑完（当背景音也算", "image": "img/option/option/20200105214011Ki5PMUEdFD1Zzb0f.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351508, "content": "在不拖进度条不开倍速的情况下完整看完", "image": "img/option/option/20200105214324RANTF4QOu932IPKb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351509, "content": "光看不行得有参与，记读书笔记/发弹幕/评论", "image": "img/option/option/20200105214441lOwN9KAYsc3HkefG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351510, "content": "看完就忘那种不算，至少能跟人复述一遍", "image": "img/option/option/20200105214559Q3bK9MFp6vV0UTwy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351512, "content": "要自己看原作，看二手的书评/影评什么都不算", "image": "img/option/option/20200105214835mJkYHOFdLsPDaoGU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351513, "content": "发表点意见，有个观后感打个分写个评语之类的", "image": "img/option/option/20200105215312i4PdaNRKypWFJX9E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351514, "content": "会查阅相关作品，看同时期的书、改编影视剧游戏", "image": "img/option/option/20200105215409q9kbdlKi8X1hg0xj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351515, "content": "以上都不算／我有其他标准", "image": "img/option/option/20200105215555rUw2M5XPRanj1ZiL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}